channel.title: Understand a Case?
channel.description:
I need help, i've got a source. (Rune-Source). It's probably the most blank source out, it's got a 8 KB client.java. When I try to add a case to make it so you can logout. (case 202.) I get this error.
[code]client.java:73: illegal start of type case 202: ^ client.java:73: ';' expected case 202: ^ client.java:73: illegal start of type case 202: ^ client.java:73: <identifier> expected case 202: ^ 4 errors Finished! Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
I don't understand how to make it recognise the case.
